Introduction

MaskOT also known as MAsk Of Thetis (마스코트) was a 5 member girl group under GBK Entertainment. The group consisted of AI, Ray, Haeri, Mina and Sophia. The group was based in Seoul, South Korea. They released a few songs in 2011, pre-debut but supposedly debuted sometime in February, 2012. Not much information is available about MaskOT.
